items.name: AUTO
desc: specifies the use of a user-defined list.
The cells are filled using a user-defined series.
If the values are all numerical, SUM is used, otherwise COUNT.

items.name: DATE
desc: specifies an arithmetic series for date values.
any date value matching the specified condition is valid.
Cell by cell, the value used to fill the cells is increased by a specified number of days

items.name: GROWTH
desc: Cell by cell, the value used to fill the cells is multiplied by a specified value.

items.name: LINEAR
desc: Cell by cell, the value used to fill the cells is increased by an additive value.

items.name: SIMPLE
desc: All cells are filled with the same value.
